title: Bluecat Adonis: Proteus NTP
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/network/bluecat
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This Check monitors the OperState of the NTP Service on bluecat devices.
 The Check will return {OK} if the Service is running, {CRITICAL} if the state is fault, {WARNING} in each other case.
 The Levels can be set with WATO.
 Also Checked are the Stratum and the Leap Seconds. Each aberrancy will lead to a {WARNING} state.

discovery:
 One service is created.
